text: Metamulciber ochreolineatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1947.BioLib.cz - Metamulciber ochreolineatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1947
